76df81e45219d498a522ad778f7b","tid":1455671,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"930a745491cd36bf3f584ee8c0359ae64d1b52e4","tid":1455671,"uid":263038,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n根本冇人衝<br />\n全部和平坐<br />\n都要咁樣封<br />\n憑咩啊？<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n64啊而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"你可以當香港係宵禁 戒嚴<br />\n只係政府無宣布咁岩"},{"pid":"ee619e98d09e3ec0f139ef1751ef3519cf17b741","tid":1455671,"uid":294020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"Copied from telegram group: <br />\n<br />\n1709 機場暫避路線（希望用唔著）<br />\n<br />\nT1有咩事記住去T2 <br />\n<br />\n*去T2方法*: <br />\n- 係離境嗰層，行去機鐵個位，有escalator落一層就係T2<br />\n- 去到T2上一層有好多餐廳、food court，有戲院！<br />\n- 去到T2，如落一層就係停車場<br />\n<br />\n*去富豪酒店 Regal Airport Hotel方法*: <br />\n- Arrival Hall A 有條行人天橋，只有一條路，行過去就係<br />\n- 現時只有Regal正門可以合法上的士、Uber  (不過今日唔知啲車入唔入到) <br />\n<br />\n*去國泰城方法* : <br />\n- Arrival Hall 任何一條樓梯落去 (有防煙門嗰啲) 就到巴士站嗰層，有幾個shuttle係去CXCity and KA House/ 民航處<br />\n<br />\n*T2去Car Park 3*<br />\n呢度係上的士熱門地點，可能可以接上車。<br />\n<br />\n註：以上地點只能暫避。<br />\n<br />\nFact Checked By 吳敏兒"},{"pid":"041e52abb353b80819788e1bd4e71f1665a8843f","tid":1455671,"uid":289493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"盡快用機鐵走，因為話6 點後到港旅客會由特別通道離開。即離境、接機大堂都危險。"},{"pid":"5a8ecb8f157e42384167d61da0e716bb62ff452c","tid":1455671,"uid":289493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"機場cut internet 啦！快！"},{"pid":"ea8b4dd343ab1f01b2bd2735e999f01e3f7c37af","tid":1455671,"uid":82110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec6438cc5723c7d924b066332e3fcaaa78fbaddf","tid":1455671,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"港珠澳行轉澳門！"},{"pid":"3f8730feaa775e88cdb4e0d7070f32b959a85738","tid":1455671,"uid":139301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"走呀！目標達成左仲唔走同送頭冇分別！<br />\n機場島唔同市區呀，唔係任佔任坐，目標達成就要走，如果唔係就走唔甩架喇！！"},{"pid":"852b60eac5254c13ad4a7ff216d04f8d89e4ed84","tid":1455671,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1aeb56a3156059fd058a931cd95ab91f875bcacf","tid":1455671,"uid":82110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f81475a102faed5063737d807c20e8ccb74c9293","tid":1455671,"uid":82110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}